TopicTitle: KSO Shuttle Mod Missions: STS 103 Munar Surface Probe Deployment and Landing

Articles.Content:
The Third of my STS KSO Shuttle Missions! STS 103's objectives are to deploy a Munar Surface Probe, return to the KSC, and successfully land the probe on the Mun.

Most of the footage is shown in 4x speed for quick viewing.

STS 104 Will bring an unmanned Minmus rover into low Kerbin orbit before returning to the KSC!
